{\listtext	2)	}Does it have documentation?\
{\listtext	3)	}Is it on GitHub?\
{\listtext	4)	}Does it have loads of outstanding issues that are months old?\
{\listtext	5)	}Does it have outstanding pull requests with no feedback?\
